list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: ~Character.java -Removed dependency on interface +added some functions for spellcasters and such ~[All of the extended files from Character] -removed all unnecessary functions leftover from the interface ~Changed how some functions call updates ~CharacterTests.java -Removed all previous tests +Added a new example test for future use in the new Character system ~DiceRollTests.java +Added tests for the new DiceRolls ~Spell.java +ReAdded support for useableBy() ~SpellTests.java +~Uncommented tests so that they pass but actuially test something +~+~+~+~ Made general changes to make the program be more self-dependent NOTE: I did not touch the UI stuff, and current bugs known are racebonuses are not loading (likely from the way that a particular class character Object is being implimented is not actuially making a class Object, but is rather remaining a Character object which does not update things properly) (Other causes are that the race is not set before racebonuses are calculated (easy fix).
